Project: Automated Windows Virtual Machine Deployment

Description:
This project provides Terraform scripts to automate the deployment of a Windows Virtual Machine on Microsoft Azure. Users can easily customize the VM specifications such as size, region, and administrator credentials.

Requirements:

Terraform installed on your machine.
An active Microsoft Azure subscription.
Usage:

Clone the repository.
Navigate to the project directory.
Run terraform init to initialize the Terraform configuration.
Create a terraform.tfvars file and provide required variables (see below).
Run terraform apply to deploy the Windows Virtual Machine.
